There you go.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:03.640
Right?

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:05.250
Now my sixth string is in tune.

00:01:05.250 --> 00:01:06.430
Then I can move on to the fifth string.

00:01:06.430 --> 00:01:07.430
Right?

