get a little crazy, and you can try to get

00:02:05.990 --> 00:02:07.470
it so perfect.

00:02:07.470 --> 00:02:08.470
You don't have to.

00:02:08.470 --> 00:02:09.470
You know.

00:02:09.470 --> 00:02:10.840
If it's close, that's pretty good.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.560
Guitars are funny that way.

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:15.230
It doesn't have to be perfect, perfect, perfect
